                </div>
                <div class="hotel-con">
                  <div class="hotel-con-list" >
                    <div class='text f-14-g-p'><p>★该行程为二选一，如果你期待感受当地风情的水上市场和铁道集市，请勾选此项。<br>★ 本日【专属车导】依旧会陪伴你整日的游玩。</div><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----丹嫩沙多1" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/5790388cecaae.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" class="image"><div class='text f-14-g-p'><br></p><p>【丹嫩沙多水上市场】</p><p>【丹嫩沙多水上市场】是极具曼谷当地风情的早间水上集市，东方刚刚露出鱼肚白，人们便划着长尾小船行至河畔赶集，尝一尝一天里最新鲜的水果，还可以在旁边丛林里【骑着大象】一览这忙碌的民俗风情。</div>                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="detail-img">
                    <div class="swiper-container detail-con-huandeng">
                      <div class="swiper-wrapper clearFix swiper-wrapper-hua">
                        <div class="swiper-slide img-list"><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----丹嫩沙多4" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/57903890cbc6c.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" ></div>
                        <div class="swiper-slide img-list"><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----丹嫩沙多1" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/5790388cecaae.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" ></div>
                        <div class="swiper-slide img-list"><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----丹嫩沙多骑大象" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/5774dbf7ece49.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" ></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                    <div class="text f-14-g-p"><br /></div>                                                                                                                                    <div class="text f-14-g-p">若恰逢周末时光，午后可以和【安帕瓦水上市场】的人们一起度过的闲散时光，在长尾船上的大排档上和河滨小岸的咖啡馆里，你见证的不仅是风景，更是这片水域人家的生活。傍晚时分，更是可以乘着小船追逐漫天萤火虫直到丛林尽头。</div>                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="detail-img">
                    <div class="swiper-container detail-con-huandeng">
                      <div class="swiper-wrapper clearFix swiper-wrapper-hua">
                        <div class="swiper-slide img-list"><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----安帕瓦4" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/579039093f9d7.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" ></div>
