                        <div class="swiper-slide img-list"><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----安帕瓦2" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/5790391a85e2e.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" ></div>
                        <div class="swiper-slide img-list"><img alt="泰国曼谷+清迈经典 | 7天6晚私家团----19" src="http://7xnvxo.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/57903921cb3db.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/750x500!/format/jpg/interlace/1/q/70" ></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                    <div class="text f-14-g-p"></p><p>【美功铁道市场】</p><p>【美功铁道市场】被称作“世界上最危险的菜市场”，小贩日出而作，日落而息，唯独多了一列轰鸣汽笛的火车每日从市场中穿行而过，从而把当地日常的生活变成了别人眼里一道举世闻名的风景。</div>                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="detail-img">
